{"tid":2201352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安局:無接獲台截獲港逃犯通知 呼籲其他司法管轄區不要窩藏逃犯","createTime":"2020-09-13T17:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T04:10:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6260cb11537d28edefa5304f5cee5a534c7b09d","tid":2201352,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:37:10.000Z","msg":"5名港人據報偷渡到台灣被陸委會扣留，保安局表示，特區政府沒有收到任何訊息，關於台灣有截獲香港逃犯，並呼籲其他司法管轄區採取明確的立場，不要窩藏在香港涉嫌犯案的罪犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保安局說，各個負責任的司法管轄區應互相合作，打擊跨境罪行，制止干犯罪行並從案發的司法管轄區逃走的罪犯，不讓他們逍遙法外，是國際認同的義務。<br />\n<br />\n台灣記者鐘聖雄在社交網站發文稱，5名香港反修例示威者，7月18日由香港出發，經東沙抵達高雄，目前正被陸委會扣留，他們無法會見律師及人權團體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2581420/保安局%3A無接獲台截獲港逃犯通知\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2581420%2F%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%253A%E7%84%A1%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%B0%E6%88%AA%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8IGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=93ca5002\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2581420/保安局%3A無接獲台截獲港逃犯通知</a><br />\n<br />\n都講咗要低調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a55f7c0fc8cd70a7d0221e05424d246bce09558","tid":2201352,"uid":168389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子收皮"},{"pid":"bcae0fdf4e1f3033be20287654d698adb0f43b1f","tid":2201352,"uid":280593,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"香港都窩藏左個"},{"pid":"e4e9b85fbef742fb2fbe37e09ee2933b0132569b","tid":2201352,"uid":258174,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:39:32.000Z